  "short_description": "KOVOCLAK is a hand-drawn 2D platformer set in a strange, poetic, and musical universe. Created by Lingouf, an electronic music producer and artist. No weapons here — only a watering can, an umbrella… and a boombox. You just have to find the right frequency !",
