  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world choked by pollution, where people live hypnotized in robotic routines, a businessman—transformed by a mysterious solar storm—decides to explore his city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/e980b34f8b871aa3166f26b797758842.apng?t=1772105866\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/e980b34f8b871aa3166f26b797758842.poster.avif?t=1772105866\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find a “real” job and earn some coins...<br>Or…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/06418ab59a7a1e0055f9571ca45f2984.poster.avif?t=1772105866\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/06418ab59a7a1e0055f9571ca45f2984.webm?t=1772105866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/06418ab59a7a1e0055f9571ca45f2984.mp4?t=1772105866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free the citizens from their digital trance and bring color back into their grey lives.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No weapons here…<br>Just a watering can, an umbrella...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/cd3173560cf188f60df9ce1034ca593c.poster.avif?t=1772105866\" width=616 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/cd3173560cf188f60df9ce1034ca593c.webm?t=1772105866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/cd3173560cf188f60df9ce1034ca593c.mp4?t=1772105866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >… and above all: a boombox.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/ee04613632a267f965a1fbab6e076b5a.poster.avif?t=1772105866\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/ee04613632a267f965a1fbab6e076b5a.webm?t=1772105866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/ee04613632a267f965a1fbab6e076b5a.mp4?t=1772105866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Record and tweak sounds, then broadcast them to interact with the world.<br>Each frequency generates a different glowing orb: some wake up the citizens, others alter the environment…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You just have to find the right frequency.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A 2D platformer inspired by 80s/90s classics, entirely hand-drawn.<br>A mix of action, exploration, and (optional) interactive dialogues, carried by offbeat, satirical humor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>KOVOCLAK</strong> offers a playfully biting look at our hyperconnected, productivity-obsessed society—while calling on your creativity to break free.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Get ready to free the city... by making some noise!</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world choked by pollution, where people live hypnotized in robotic routines, a businessman—transformed by a mysterious solar storm—decides to explore his city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/e980b34f8b871aa3166f26b797758842.apng?t=1772105866\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/e980b34f8b871aa3166f26b797758842.poster.avif?t=1772105866\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find a “real” job and earn some coins...<br>Or…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/06418ab59a7a1e0055f9571ca45f2984.poster.avif?t=1772105866\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/06418ab59a7a1e0055f9571ca45f2984.webm?t=1772105866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/06418ab59a7a1e0055f9571ca45f2984.mp4?t=1772105866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free the citizens from their digital trance and bring color back into their grey lives.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No weapons here…<br>Just a watering can, an umbrella...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/cd3173560cf188f60df9ce1034ca593c.poster.avif?t=1772105866\" width=616 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/cd3173560cf188f60df9ce1034ca593c.webm?t=1772105866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/cd3173560cf188f60df9ce1034ca593c.mp4?t=1772105866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >… and above all: a boombox.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/ee04613632a267f965a1fbab6e076b5a.poster.avif?t=1772105866\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/ee04613632a267f965a1fbab6e076b5a.webm?t=1772105866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/ee04613632a267f965a1fbab6e076b5a.mp4?t=1772105866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Record and tweak sounds, then broadcast them to interact with the world.<br>Each frequency generates a different glowing orb: some wake up the citizens, others alter the environment…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You just have to find the right frequency.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A 2D platformer inspired by 80s/90s classics, entirely hand-drawn.<br>A mix of action, exploration, and (optional) interactive dialogues, carried by offbeat, satirical humor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>KOVOCLAK</strong> offers a playfully biting look at our hyperconnected, productivity-obsessed society—while calling on your creativity to break free.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Get ready to free the city... by making some noise!</strong></p>",
